 those offering words of support in the release were Michael Govan, the dir=
ector of LACMA; Lana
Negrete, the mayor of Santa Monica; Katherine Fleming, the president and C.=
E.O. of the J. Paul Getty Trust; and several high-profile gallerists from L=
