=C2=A0

=E2=80=9CThe strong feedback we=E2=80=99ve received,=E2=80=9D the statement=
 points out, =E2=80=9Chas highlighted the fair=E2=80=99s key role as a plat=
form for creativity, connection, and resilience, now more than ever. Togeth=
er with our participants and partners,
we are developing initiatives to aid recovery efforts.=E2=80=9D As I noted =
