=9Chas highlighted the fair=E2=80=99s key role as a platform for creativity=
, connection, and resilience, now more than ever. Together with our partici=
pants and partners,
we are developing initiatives to aid recovery efforts.=E2=80=9D As I noted =
Friday, this is good news=E2=80=94the art world doing its part to support i=
ts own.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p styl=
e=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">I look forward to doing my part. Let me k=
now if you=E2=80=99ll be in L.A. for Felix and Frieze.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D=
